之贈與。 八、每月應製作收入支出帳目。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDV/109%2c%e5%8f%b8%e5%9f%b7%e6%b6%88%e5%82%b5%e6%9b%b4%2c225%2c20211012/pdf"},"JID":"TPDV,109,司執消債更,225,20211012","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"司執消債更","JNO":"225","JDATE":"20211012","JTITLE":"更生事件"}